About Us
Welcome to your SOCIAL KORNER!
"Where the good life meets the fun times"
"Let's travel around the world without leaving the Korner", and discover a new cultural experience formed by diverse culinary masterpieces and a wide variety of mixology drinks.
Korner 67 Kitchen Bar has been created to promote connections and bring family and friends together around a table full of the best flavors of our "Tapas Style" dishes.

Private Events
Book an Event
For all inquiries, please fill out the form below and we’ll be in touch soon.
Inquire Now
Book our space for your next event and make it unforgettable
At KORNER67, we strive to make your event planning process as smooth and stress-free as possible. When you book your event with us, we'll assign you a dedicated Event Coordinator who will be your main point of contact from start to finish.
Our Event Coordinator will work with you every step of the way to ensure your event is a success. Whether you're selecting items from our menu or creating a personalized menu with your Coordinator, we'll make sure that every detail is taken care of. Our sommelier and spirits expert can also assist you in creating the perfect food and drink pairing, while our beverage experts can create a customized drink menu to suit your needs.
We understand the importance of timing, and we'll work with you to make sure that your event runs smoothly and ends on time. If you'd like to extend your event, we'll do our best to accommodate your request (additional fees may apply). Please note that any event extension is subject to availability in our restaurant.
